et me my slippers. Stare at you like that. He wouldn't have touched us but you know his voice was - he would have been strict but - mother wouldn't - mother was boss. Oh yes, she - she could always - though they got on very well together - she was really 
- the mainstay of the home - the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11023217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 When he was home was he home for very long periods?
