No. He wasn't. Because - when he was - would be about - a fortnight I should think. The last - line he was at he was away a month and for - fortnight at home. That was a - a - a very nice trip.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11023217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 You say when he was home he was happy to be home and you were all happy to have him there?
