\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11023217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 In what sort of way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160330 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 Well -
