s Doll - she'd get in a temper }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 now and again. She was more of course - cross patch but - the others were all - you know - no, we were always - I never remember really a bad quarrel.
