\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11023217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 Harry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3160330 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 No, my moth - my sister - Sarah. Yes. When I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8463588 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396  she bought every stitch that I wore - wouldn't let
 anybody else do it - she sent the silk home from Idian for me wedding dress and - course it had to be made here and - veil, everything shoes, gloves everything - underclothes, everything. That was the eldest sister. Of course she was then - getting on.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11023217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 As a child who did you play with?
