I think I was rather a quiet - didn't play with - oh there was a neighbour who I went to school with, name of Hetty Skeins - we used - she used to call for me and sometimes I used to call for her. But - mostly it 
was - she had to call for me - I'd be the latest. I - I'm afraid I wasn't very regular at school because I had in between help mother. I being the eldest one - girl then. But I did - it didn't have many - no, I don't think I had any other - other - yes I 
did, there was another - oh I don't think I really keen on her but - this was - her mother was my mother's - friend and my mother - knew their grand mother, you know - three generations there, but we kept all - all and - intact that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11023217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 Did you play mainly with your brothers and sisters and the little girl next door?
