Well - was this - was this Mr James he was very nice indeed and - he came to my place and he - his - he admired a jug that I'd got - he offered me five pound for it so I gave it to him - that he was a colle
ctor of - what would you call it - Daltonware wasn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11023217 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 What class would you say he was in?
