ople were real ladies - or a gentleman well of course there was as I say, one or two that we did - like you you would come to the house not to be - permanent but - as I say, this Mr James come to our house and he was this thing on the pedestal and he - he
 was collecting it and as far as my knowledge he had that on his dinning room ma}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4744601\charrsid2379396 n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9327244\charrsid2379396 tle}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
